Revision history for RT-Extension-QueueListCustom

0.03  2026-05-21
    - Per-lifecycle queue visibility: hide individual queues per user
    - Empty-queue hiding toggle (Show empty queues preference)
    - Collapsible lifecycle sections with saved collapsed state per user
    - Drag-and-drop lifecycle ordering on preferences page (Sortable.js)
    - Manual reload button fetches fresh ticket counts via AJAX
    - Last-loaded timestamp shown at the bottom of the portlet
    - Configurable auto-refresh (2 / 5 / 10 / 20 / 60 / 120 minutes)
    - Fixed: license value in Makefile.PL (gpl2 → gpl)
    - Fixed: collapse arrow now appears before lifecycle name in portlet header
    - Added META.yml; added perl_version 5.010 requirement

0.01  2026-05-21
    - Initial release
    - Per-user, per-lifecycle status configuration via dedicated preferences page
    - Portlet shows only queues the current user has ShowTicket access to
    - Falls back to initial + active statuses when no preferences are saved
    - Gear icon links directly to the preferences page
